{
  "stem": "22840.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From the military point of view, it was the most foolish thing which can happen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you look at the map, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the area of the uprising would sever the lines of retreat of the Germans from southern Europe, back through Poland to Germany.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We couldn't allow such a base for allies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was clear that if something like that happened, it will be-- have to be crushed militarily.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Having said that-- just look at the map.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Having said that, the Russian army was just across the border.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Russian army would want it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They could have intervened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the slaughter could have stopped.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know what the political aims of the Russians were.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I don't think the Russians were averse to the idea of weakening the infrastructure of independent politics in the areas they wanted to take control over.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I think they callously let the Germans slaughter the Slovaks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the-- and their own forces, which were sent, and the Western forces, and let the Slovaks slaughter some of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They showed it, in the future, that the Russians are ready to fight to the last Bulgarian, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I think that was politically a callous decision by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But that's my interpretation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The bottom line is that militarily, the German had to crush it because it was endangering the main lines of communication with their other forces.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They invaded Slovakia, took over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they crushed the rebellion.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Through the air.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And from-- not only from the Russians, also from the Western powers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was an air-- airfield in Tri Duby-- that's the name of the place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were regular flights there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were also drops.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There's also, you know, smuggling through the mountains from the Russian side.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
